name: FDOT District 5 -- Fire Stations, Florida, 2006
description: This dataset contains fire stations and emergency medical service (EMS) centers locations for the East Central Florida (FDOT District 5) area. This GIS layer was produced by Data Transfer Solutions (DTS) under contract with FDOT District 5 in 2006. This is one of many layers that fall into the general category of "sociocultural" GIS data.
